The project is available as "software as a service" in free beta version:

http://tooljar.biz

NOTE: 
1) Please do not use this code at this stage: it's not usable! Use the master branch instead

2) This version requires php5-intl installed on your system http://php.net/manual/en/intl.installation.php



To download this version do:

mkdir /tmp/git
cd /tmp/git
git clone https://github.com/damko/MyClientBase-SB.git
cd MyClientBase-SB
git fetch
git checkout --track -b new-ui origin/new_ui

git submodule init
git submodule update
cd sparks/ion_auth/2.3.3
git checkout contact_engine
